publisher			SEGA							
publish_time	 2011年3月4日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Hey hey, come on over and have some fun with Crrrrrazy Taxi! Barrel through traffic packed streets, hurdle off parking garages, and Crazy Combo your way to Crazy Money in a wild frantic race to scare up the most fares. In Crazy Taxi, time is money, and only the Craziest Cabbies come out victorious.						Features													  Two Game Modes – Arcade Mode and Original Mode for a variety of gameplay, and 16 Mini Games to hone your taxi driving skills.							  Extra large hills for extra long hang time							  Parked transporters with conveniently angled ramps							  Tall cliffs and parking garages with steep drops							  Painfully slow buses and cable cars to frustrate and annoy							  Occasional deep sea exploration opportunities!																		
